data.description: Welcome home! This lovely 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch with beautiful bay windows sits on a quiet cul de sac with no neighbors behind you. Vinyl flooring throughout except for the kitchen and bathroom. New flooring has been installed in the living room, hallway, and kitchen. There is an attached 2-car garage, and the walls are insulated. The roof is BRAND NEW, and the furnace is less than a year old. The AC and HWH are less than 5 years old. Newer siding. The huge backyard is fully fenced and there is a deck in the front and back of the home. Need extra storage? There is a shed in the backyard that will solve that problem. Don't miss out on this beautiful, affordable home located minutes away from 80/94, making your commute to Chicago or Michigan very convenient. With a little TLC, you can make this home your own in no time. Schedule your showing today!
